betterquesting:10.desc:8:
What is this?

If you're having trouble finding mystical flowers, perhaps they have always been in front of you! Look for any mushrooms out of place that shimmer a little bit. Look for tall grass that might shimmer a bit.
Can you see it? Probably not because you're in sand right now.
Get down there and start mining!

betterquesting:10.name:8: Maybe there is a better way?
betterquesting:10.desc:8: Perhaps I could make my own tools to do it better?
A whole new world with all sorts of stuff in it!
Learn to look at the stars. Nothing more.
